---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navigation from "../../components/Navigation.astro";
import ContactForm from "../../components/ContactForm.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Work With Us - Medcalf Software Solutions"
  description="Scoped engagements with clear deliverables. Discovery Sprints, Build Sprints, and Advisory retainers for AI, graph database, and automation projects."
>
  <Navigation />

  <main class="services-landing">
    <article class="container">
      <header class="page-header">
        <h1>How We Work Together</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          <em>Scoped engagements with clear deliverables</em>
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="page-content">
        <p class="page-intro">
          Start with a free hour. If there's a fit, we scope a focused sprint
          with a defined deliverable, timeline, and fixed price. No ambiguity.
          No open-ended retainers. You know exactly what you're getting.
        </p>

        <div class="tiers-grid">
          <div class="service-tier service-tier--free">
            <div class="tier-top">
              <h2>Free Consult</h2>
              <p class="pricing">Free</p>
              <p class="timing">1 hour</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tier-body">
              <ul>
                <li>1-on-1 conversation with Ben Medcalf</li>
                <li>Assess fit for AI, graph databases, or automation</li>
                <li>Actionable recommendation: build, wait, or look elsewhere</li>
                <li>Rough scope and effort estimate if there's a fit</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Figuring out if we're the right partner — zero risk.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="https://calendar.app.google/jzac8cPcXKKtnVQ39" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="tier-cta">Book a Free Hour</a>
          </div>

          <div class="service-tier">
            <div class="tier-top">
              <h2>Discovery Sprint</h2>
              <p class="pricing">$3,500</p>
              <p class="timing">fixed · 1 week</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tier-body">
              <ul>
                <li>Technical feasibility assessment</li>
                <li>Architecture recommendation with trade-offs</li>
                <li>Implementation roadmap with effort estimates</li>
                <li>Go/no-go recommendation with honest reasoning</li>
                <li>Written deliverable you own and keep</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> De-risking an idea before committing real budget.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/#contact" class="tier-cta">Book a Discovery Sprint</a>
          </div>

          <div class="service-tier">
            <div class="tier-top">
              <h2>Build Sprint</h2>
              <p class="pricing">$6k&ndash;$15k</p>
              <p class="timing">fixed · 2&ndash;6 weeks</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tier-body">
              <ul>
                <li>End-to-end implementation of a scoped deliverable</li>
                <li>Testing and validation suite</li>
                <li>Documentation and handoff materials</li>
                <li>Weekly progress updates</li>
                <li>2 weeks of bug-fix support after delivery</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Shipping a working feature, integration, or pipeline.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/#contact" class="tier-cta">Start a Build Sprint</a>
          </div>

          <div class="service-tier">
            <div class="tier-top">
              <h2>Advisory</h2>
              <p class="pricing">$2,000</p>
              <p class="timing">monthly · ongoing</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tier-body">
              <ul>
                <li>60-minute strategy call each month</li>
                <li>Same-day async responses via message or email</li>
                <li>Architecture and code reviews</li>
                <li>Technical decision-making support</li>
                <li>Priority scheduling when you're ready for a new sprint</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Teams that want ongoing expert guidance between sprints.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/#contact" class="tier-cta">Schedule a Call</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <section class="how-it-works">
          <h2>How It Works</h2>
          <p><strong>We talk.</strong> Tell me what you're trying to accomplish. No commitment, no pitch.</p>
          <p><strong>I scope it.</strong> If there's a fit, I'll propose a specific sprint with deliverables and fixed price.</p>
          <p><strong>I build it.</strong> You get weekly updates and a working result at the end.</p>
          <p><strong>You decide what's next.</strong> Another sprint? Advisory retainer? Nothing? Your call.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Recent Work</h2>
          <ul class="recent-work">
            <li>
              <a href="/blog/honey-i-vibe-coded-the-c-suite"
                >Domain-Specific PDF Extraction with ChatGPT</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/blog/StatFoundry-Part1"
                >Modeling the NFL as a Knowledge Graph in Neo4j</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/blog/StatFoundry-Part3"
                >Query Expansion Architecture for Neo4j and React</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

  <ContactForm />
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .services-landing {
    padding-top: 120px;
    padding-bottom: 80px;
    background-color: #fff;
  }

  .services-landing .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #666;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .page-content {
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .page-intro {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    color: #444;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .tiers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .service-tier {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-top: 4px solid #23aa57;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .service-tier:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .service-tier--free {
    border-top-color: #2563eb;
  }

  .tier-top {
    padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  .service-tier h2 {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    color: #23aa57;
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .service-tier--free h2 {
    color: #2563eb;
  }

  .pricing {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .timing {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #888;
    margin: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .tier-body {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .service-tier ul {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .service-tier li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: #555;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .service-tier li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #23aa57;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .service-tier--free li::before {
    color: #2563eb;
  }

  .best-for {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: #666;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .how-it-works h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem;
    color: #333;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #23aa57;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .how-it-works p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: #444;
  }

  .tier-cta {
    display: block;
    margin: auto 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
    background-color: #23aa57;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .tier-cta:hover {
    background-color: #1d8f49;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .service-tier--free .tier-cta {
    background-color: #2563eb;
  }

  .service-tier--free .tier-cta:hover {
    background-color: #1d4ed8;
  }

  .page-content > section:last-child h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem;
    color: #333;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #23aa57;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .recent-work {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .recent-work li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .recent-work a {
    color: #23aa57;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .recent-work a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-landing {
      padding-top: 100px;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .page-content {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .tiers-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .service-tier h2 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .pricing {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .how-it-works h2,
    .page-content > section:last-child h2 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }
  }
</style>
